The paper discusses the security challenges and solutions for IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the use of intelligent mechanisms for intrusion detection, which can be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and security and privacy (cs.SI). Finally, the paper provides a security framework and enhancement techniques, which can be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE).
